OL,3,CBread and beer prices set to rise as
OL,4,Cstormy winter cripples UK crops
OL,6,FThe price of bread, beer and biscuits
OL,7,Fmay rise this year the unusually wet
OL,8,Fweather seen over autumn and winter
OL,9,Fcould hit UK harvests by almost a
OL,10,Ffifth, research suggests.
OL,12,FThe Energy and Climate Intelligence
OL,13,FUnit (ECIU) analysed the crop area
OL,14,Fforecasts from the Agriculture and
OL,15,FHorticulture Development Board (AHBD)
OL,16,Fas well as government yield data.
OL,18,FIt found that production of wheat,
OL,19,Fbarley, oats and oilseed rape could
OL,20,Ffall by four million tonnes compared
OL,21,Fto 2023 ` a reduction of 17.5%.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/9
