OL,3,CBread and beer prices set to rise as
OL,4,Cstormy winter cripples UK crops
OL,6,FThe decline may be more than five
OL,7,Fmillion ` or 21.2% ` if compared to
OL,8,Fthe average production of the years
OL,9,F2015 to 2023, the analysis also
OL,10,Fsuggests.
OL,12,FIt comes as the unusually wet autumn
OL,13,Fresulted in lower levels of planting,
OL,14,Fwhile relentless storms and flooding
OL,15,Fover winter led to even more losses
OL,16,Ffor British farmers.
