OL,3,CBread and beer prices set to rise as
OL,4,Cstormy winter cripples UK crops
OL,6,FTom Lancaster, land analyst at ECIU,
OL,7,Fsaid there is a "real risk" that the
OL,8,Fprice of bread, beer and biscuits
OL,9,Fcould increase if the poor harvest
OL,10,Fleads to higher costs.
OL,12,FThe warning comes just as food prices
OL,13,Fare beginning to fall following
OL,14,Fskyrocketing inflation sparked by the
OL,15,Fglobal gas price crisis.
OL,17,FWheat production could be hit
OL,18,Fparticularly hard, with the ECIU
OL,19,Festimating a fall of more than a
OL,20,Fquarter ` 26.5% ` compared to 2023.
