OL,3,CBread and beer prices set to rise as
OL,4,Cstormy winter cripples UK crops
OL,6,FThis is because milling wheat used to
OL,7,Fmake bread needs to meet higher
OL,8,Fquality requirements that will be more
OL,9,Fdifficult for farmers to achieve with
OL,10,Fthe wet weather.
OL,12,FLast week, the head of Associated
OL,13,FBritish Foods ` one of the UK's
OL,14,Fbiggest breadmakers, which owns
OL,15,FKingsmill and Ryvita ` warned of
OL,16,Fpotentially higher prices if the rise
OL,17,Fin the cost of domestic grains is not
OL,18,Foffset by larger harvests abroad.
