OL,3,CBread and beer prices set to rise as
OL,4,Cstormy winter cripples UK crops
OL,6,FWith the wet weather continuing to
OL,7,Fhamper the planting of spring crops
OL,8,Flike barley, brewers and distillers
OL,9,Fmay also see higher costs, leading to
OL,10,Fan increase in the cost of a pint, the
OL,11,FECIU said.
OL,13,FColin Chappell, an arable farmer from
OL,14,FLincolnshire and member of the Nature-
OL,15,FFriendly Farming Network (NFFN), said:
OL,16,F"It's had a massive impact on us.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/9
