OL,3,CBread and beer prices set to rise as
OL,4,Cstormy winter cripples UK crops
OL,6,F"We went through the winter with
OL,7,Fvirtually nothing viable drilled, and
OL,8,Fwhile it's now dry enough to plant
OL,9,Fsome fields some of them are so bad I
OL,10,Fdon't think they'll get drilled this
OL,11,Fyear. The situation is very hit and
OL,12,Fmiss."
OL,14,FIt comes as the National Farmers'
OL,15,FUnion (NFU) recently said extreme
OL,16,Fweather presents one of the biggest
OL,17,Fthreats to UK food security.
OL,19,FWarmer wetter winters similar to this
OL,20,Fpast year are expected to increase in
OL,21,Ffrequency as the climate warms.
