OL,3,CBread and beer prices set to rise as
OL,4,Cstormy winter cripples UK crops
OL,6,FNoting that half of British food comes
OL,7,Ffrom abroad, Mr Lancaster said the
OL,8,Fgovernment will have to ensure farmers
OL,9,Fboth in the UK and abroad are
OL,10,Fsupported.
OL,12,FMr Chappell said the new Sustainable
OL,13,FFarming Incentive from the government
OL,14,Fis how his farm will survive in the
OL,15,Fcoming years.
OL,17,F"The climate is making farming on
OL,18,Fheavy clay soils like mine very
OL,19,Fdifficult and quite demoralising," he
OL,20,Fadded.
