OL,3,CBread and beer prices set to rise as
OL,4,Cstormy winter cripples UK crops
OL,6,FWilliam Kendall, an East Anglian
OL,7,Ffarmer who turned Green & Blacks into
OL,8,Fa global chocolate brand, said:
OL,9,F"Regenerative farming methods, when
OL,10,Fproperly followed, greatly enhance the
OL,11,Fsoil's capacity to hold water and
OL,12,Ftherefore prevent saturation and run-
OL,13,Foff at times of prolonged heavy
OL,14,Frainfall.
OL,16,F"Not only does this mean better crops,
OL,17,Fproduced at a lower cost for the
OL,18,Ffarmer, but it ensures that the
OL,19,Fchances of the flash flooding
OL,20,Fdownstream we have seen this winter
OL,21,Fare greatly diminished."
